  "title": "Medical Sales Representative ( Entry Level ) #HHL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>To meet monthly sales goals by finding leads, building a client list, and turning prospects into clients.</li><li>To identify key decision-makers at clinics to promote Cord Tissue Storage</li><li>To build and maintain good relationships with clients, partners, and customers.</li><li>To follow up with customers from sign-up to delivery, before and after sales.</li><li>To handle leads by setting up home presentations, organizing Kit boxes</li><li>To attend and represent the company at baby events, seminars, and other relevant functions.</li><li>To complete other tasks as assigned by supervisors.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Degree in  Biological Science / Biomedical Engineering or other equivalent</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Good track record of CCA</li><li>People-oriented</li><li>Resourceful and self-motivated.</li><li>No prior experience needed</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume  to alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl             </p><p>➖             </p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong             </p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)             </p><p>alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>",
